\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 28, 2026</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104agg1665702533827.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/agg1665702533827.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/agg1665702533827.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"agg1665702533827\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Returns a constant string denoting the object type.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"agg1665702533827__topic_d128096e1_d128097e1_d128098e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"agg1665702533827__p_d128099e1_d128100e1_d128101e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Object</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">.<span class=\"keyword apiname\">getType()</span>\n</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"agg1665702533827__section_w1914ab1b5b3_w1915ab1b5_w1916ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1080982e64\">Arguments </h2>\n<p class=\"p\">None</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"agg1665702533827__section_w1917ab1b5b5_w1918ab1b5_w1919ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1080982e73\">Return Value</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"agg1665702533827__p_d128111e1_d128112e1_d128113e1\">Returns one of the following constants (shown with\n        their internal representation):</p>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"agg1665702533827__parml_kfw_rw3_dwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">uniface.TYPE_DSPINSTANCE (C)</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">For <code class=\"ph codeph\">uniface.Instance </code>objects</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">uniface.TYPE_ENTITY (E)</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">For  <code class=\"ph codeph\">uniface.Entity</code> objects</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">uniface.TYPE_OCCURRENCE (O)</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">For <code class=\"ph codeph\">uniface.Occurence</code> objects</dd>\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">uniface.TYPE_FIELD (F)</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">For <code class=\"ph codeph\">uniface.Field</code> objects</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"agg1665702533827__section_w1920ab1b5b7_w1921ab1b5_w1922ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1080982e133\">Exceptions</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following exceptions may be thrown:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">uniface.InvalidDataObjectException</code></li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dtg1665702533539.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.Instance</a><p>The uniface.Instance object provides access to selected properties and methods of the component instance that it represents.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/reb1665702537007.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.Entity</a><p>The uniface.Entity object provides access to selected properties of the component entity that it represents. It is returned by the getEntities and getEntity functions of the uniface.Instance and uniface.Occurrence objects.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hfh1665702535808.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.Occurrence</a><p>The uniface.Occurrence object provides access to selected properties of the occurrence that it represents. It is returned by the getOccurrence function of the uniface.Entity object.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dlx1665702535259.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.Field</a><p>The uniface.Field object provides access to selected properties of the field that it represents. It is returned by the getField function of uniface.Occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/shk1665703139073.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.InvalidDataObjectException</a><p>Exception thrown if the object on which the function is called is no longer valid.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525669\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525669\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "getType() Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 28, 2026 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Returns a constant string denoting the object type. Object . getType() Arguments None Return Value Returns one of the following constants (shown with their internal representation): uniface.TYPE_DSPINSTANCE (C) For uniface.Instance objects uniface.TYPE_ENTITY (E) For uniface.Entity objects uniface.TYPE_OCCURRENCE (O) For uniface.Occurence objects uniface.TYPE_FIELD (F) For uniface.Field objects Exceptions The following exceptions may be thrown: uniface.InvalidDataObjectException Related Links uniface.Instance The uniface.Instance object provides access to selected properties and methods of the component instance that it represents. uniface.Entity The uniface.Entity object provides access to selected properties of the component entity that it represents. It is returned by the getEntities and getEntity functions of the uniface.Instance and uniface.Occurrence objects. uniface.Occurrence The uniface.Occurrence object provides access to selected properties of the occurrence that it represents. It is returned by the getOccurrence function of the uniface.Entity object. uniface.Field The uniface.Field object provides access to selected properties of the field that it represents. It is returned by the getField function of uniface.Occurrence. uniface.InvalidDataObjectException Exception thrown if the object on which the function is called is no longer valid. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}